      <title>Hexo + Github 搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="/2020/06/18/article-title/"/>
      <url>/2020/06/18/article-title/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Hexo-Github-搭建个人博客"><a href="#Hexo-Github-搭建个人博客" class="headerlink" title="Hexo + Github 搭建个人博客"></a><center>Hexo + Github 搭建个人博客</center></h2><a id="more"></a><p>只能从二级目录（##）开始</p><center><span class='p large red'>这</span><span class='p large yellow'>是</span><span class='p large green'>我</span><span class='p large black'>老</span><span class='p large blue'>婆</span></center><p><img src="/images/xinmuyouzi.jpg" alt=""></p><p>1.基本教程：<br><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/111614119" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/111614119</a></p><p>2.网站主题模板美化：<br><a href="https://volantis.js.org/v2/tag-plugins/#Image" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://volantis.js.org/v2/tag-plugins/#Image</a><br>2.1 .md文件中使用本地图片：<br><del><a href="https://github.com/boboidream/hexo-easy-images" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/boboidream/hexo-easy-images</a><br>安装完这个插件后直接在source/_post下面建立一个同.md文件同名的文件夹 将图片放里面 然后在.md里面引用为![](../.md文件名/图片名.jpg)</del><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/u012307002/article/details/51298705" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/u012307002/article/details/51298705</a><br>在source下新建一个文件夹(images) 然后把图片放里面<br>在.md文件中直接就用![](/images/xinmuyouzi.jpg)  从这个文件夹中调用<br>2.2 免费图床<br><a href="https://sm.ms/home/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://sm.ms/home/</a><br>body: [article, related_posts, comments]<br>sidebar: [news, related_posts, donate, repos, toc]</p><p>分享到qq 空间 和微博在xd-zhengBlog\themes\volantis\layout_third-party\share.ejs中设置</p><p>网站运营时间：<br><a href="https://juejin.im/post/5dbe8ea951882520cb1a2747#heading-12" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://juejin.im/post/5dbe8ea951882520cb1a2747#heading-12</a><br>显示部分放在最后else中替换<br>然后theme目录下config文件中footer中把 br 选上</p>]]></content>
      
      
